{"tid":2073097,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"日本《全職獵人》FANS每日實況揮正拳1000次直到連載重啟！","createTime":"2020-06-21T05:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T07:32:25.000Z","uid":38539,"like":77,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"2a942df7c8c4cf8108031f2fc9c84ddfdb66e43f","tid":2073097,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gQkupwA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgQkupwA.png&h=4426a89b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你等，我等，大家都在等。《HUNTER X HUNTER》（以下以《獵人》代稱）作者冨樫義博自週刊少年 Jump 2019 年 1 號宣佈休刊後，到現在還沒重啟連載，很有可能會破當時2014～2016 年休刊 80 週的記錄。<br />\n<br />\n而日本有位《獵人》粉絲「樽江突撃」自 1 月 16 日起發起「每天揮 1 千次正拳直到《獵人》復刊」，並在個人 YouTube 頻道開啟實況。這個運動正是致敬《獵人》角色艾薩克．尼特羅的「每日一萬次滿懷感激的正拳」，雖然次數少了一個零，其決心依舊值得讓網友敬佩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WKd3SK-id6E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWKd3SK-id6E&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y1HO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=8ac99349\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WKd3SK-id6E</a><br />\n<br />\n透過社群分享，近期樽江突撃的正拳影片人氣高漲，18 日上傳的揮正拳影片觀看人數已突破 2 萬，獲得眾多網友支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/akinosin74/status/1262229696009211904?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fakinosin74%2Fstatus%2F1262229696009211904%3Fs%3D20&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y1HO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=840b944c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fakinosin74%2Fstatus%2F1262229696009211904%3Fs%3D20&h=fa682816\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/akinosin74/status/1262229696009211904?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.4gamers.com.tw/news/detail/43191/when-will-hunter-x-hunter-start-in-2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.4gamers.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F43191%2Fwhen-will-hunter-x-hunter-start-in-2020&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y1HO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=1c